Stop and Shop Cos Inc said sales for thefour weeks ended February 28 for its Bradlees DiscountDepartment Stores Division were up six pct to 104 mln dlrs from98 mln dlrs a year before, with same-store sales up three pct.     The company said the modest comparable store sales increasewas due to a combination of difficult weather conditions in theNortheast, a later Easter this year and a possible slowing inconsumer demand. Reuter&#3;